{"tid":2007797,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國共和黨成立調查中國小組 主席妻子卻被揭持有騰訊股票","createTime":"2020-05-08T14:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T13:51:50.000Z","uid":28765,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2797a2309b87f2bb4dfee5503d7b8bb24716dc7b","tid":2007797,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:14:54.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國眾議院共和黨領袖麥卡錫（Kevin McCarthy）今天在記者會上宣布，因應中國在經濟影響、科技野心等造成的威脅，將成立15人中國工作小組（China Task Force），並指派共和黨首席議員麥考爾（Michael McCaul）擔任主席一職，但主席麥考爾的妻子卻被爆料出竟持有中國大型科技公司「騰訊」的股票，引起外界譁然。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/05/08/php4A06ve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F05%2F08%2Fphp4A06ve.jpg&h=233594e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，共和黨領袖麥卡錫表示，將會從10個眾議院委員會中挑選出15位議員，成立「中國工作小組」以應對來自北京的各種地緣政治威脅，並針對目前中國各大議題，例如中方對美大專院校和新聞媒體、對美政府及盟友的經濟威脅，以及爭奪科技優勢等作為展開調查，其中對武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）的起源與傳播尤為關注。<br />\n<br />\n不料身為中國工作小組主席，共和黨首席議員麥考爾，卻遭美媒《政客》（Politico）踢爆麥考爾的妻子琳達（Linda McCaul）持有中國大型科技公司「騰訊」股票。據報導麥考爾交出的一份資產報告，其中一項細目中顯示，在2月份時曾購買了「騰訊」公司價值5萬至10萬美金（147萬至295萬元新台幣）的股票震驚眾人。對此，麥考爾的律師出面澄清表示，騰訊公司股票的持有人是他的妻子琳達，並未在他名下，更指出該股票是經由第三方經理在沒有接受指示下所購買的。<br />\n<br />\n麥考爾在工作小組成立時表示，在共產黨的極權統治下，中國已成為美國戰略敵人（strategic adversary），同時也是目前最重大的外交政策挑戰，而中國疑似隱匿疫情，也再度讓世界開始意識到，北京所帶來的威脅，遠不止經濟科技的影響，為全世界敲響警鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3159554\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3159554&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQOzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=498c0640\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3159554&h=341388d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3159554</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.com/news/2020/05/07/mike-mccaul-stock-in-chinese-company-243602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F05%2F07%2Fmike-mccaul-stock-in-chinese-company-243602&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQOzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=32150f94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.politico.com/news/2020/05/07/mike-mccaul-stock-in-chinese-company-243602</a>"},{"pid":"65e96a89908ac8ef23aa7d411b1f4ca393007570","tid":2007797,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:15:37.000Z","msg":"我屌"},{"pid":"65367989ec84eaf9e59babcb5b856735a20dd054","tid":2007797,"uid":228995,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"香港有幾多黃絲/泛民議員有hold 700、阿里同美團？"},{"pid":"e4cb8d16c5e9b5b2a67e38b68a9e82f23e053685","tid":2007797,"uid":5822,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:18:11.000Z","msg":"股票姐屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a31c332575b526dc10c68d62ab8a417857b5f5","tid":2007797,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65367989ec84eaf9e59babcb5b856735a20dd054","tid":2007797,"uid":228995,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"香港有幾多黃絲/泛民議員有hold 700、阿里同美團？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，我all in LMT"},{"pid":"d5948685e5da02bef350b6f40acc62dbcc405018","tid":2007797,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:21:54.000Z","msg":"好事<br />\n如果真係有人屌代表民眾都aware<br />\n換咗佢再做好due diligence就得"},{"pid":"da4d95908c4bbb10f7c4a78a8e6e13d509708263","tid":2007797,"uid":25468,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e4cb8d16c5e9b5b2a67e38b68a9e82f23e053685","tid":2007797,"uid":5822,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:18:11.000Z","msg":"股票姐屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"政治就係咁 , 你把口話要對付支那 , 但又投資落支那 , 觀感會好差"},{"pid":"8b5a8697d06de7a40674e453701dd7413a4cc16d","tid":2007797,"uid":14494,"l